They were told they were
being given a sugar pill.

00:36:51.310 --> 00:36:51.710 align:middle line:90%
>>HOROWITZ: That's right.

00:36:51.710 --> 00:36:52.080 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Take it from here.

00:36:52.080 --> 00:36:54.378 align:middle line:84%
>>HOROWITZ: There this is
the so-called honest placebo

00:36:54.378 --> 00:36:56.920 align:middle line:84%
study that was conducted several
years ago at Harvard Medical

00:36:56.920 --> 00:36:58.185 align:middle line:90%
School.

00:36:58.185 --> 00:37:00.310 align:middle line:84%
Harvard took a group of
subjects who were suffering

00:37:00.310 --> 00:37:02.680 align:middle line:90%
from irritable bowel syndrome.

00:37:02.680 --> 00:37:04.838 align:middle line:84%
One group of subjects
was given nothing.

00:37:04.838 --> 00:37:06.130 align:middle line:90%
They were just a control group.

00:37:06.130 --> 00:37:10.030 align:middle line:84%
Another group of subjects was
given effectively a sugar pill.

00:37:10.030 --> 00:37:13.780 align:middle line:84%
And this group of subjects was
told transparently and upfront,

00:37:13.780 --> 00:37:15.670 align:middle line:90%
this is a sugar pill.

00:37:15.670 --> 00:37:18.320 align:middle line:84%
You are receiving an
inert, inactive substance.

00:37:18.320 --> 00:37:24.570 align:middle line:84%
59% of those subjects reported
significant and lasting relief.

00:37:24.570 --> 00:37:26.920 align:middle line:90%
It was absolutely extraordinary.

00:37:26.920 --> 00:37:29.320 align:middle line:84%
And my hat is really off
to these researchers,

00:37:29.320 --> 00:37:32.200 align:middle line:84%
because not only did they
structure a very innovative

00:37:32.200 --> 00:37:36.910 align:middle line:84%
experiment, but they held
back from judging the results.

00:37:36.910 --> 00:37:39.430 align:middle line:84%
They said, look, we found
something extraordinary.

00:37:39.430 --> 00:37:42.490 align:middle line:84%
The placebo effect
works transparently.

00:37:42.490 --> 00:37:43.720 align:middle line:90%
It works.

00:37:43.720 --> 00:37:45.400 align:middle line:90%
Now what do we do with it?

00:37:45.400 --> 00:37:46.240 align:middle line:90%
Why?

00:37:46.240 --> 00:37:49.030 align:middle line:84%
Isn't that a wonderful Question
