00:37:53.933 --> 00:37:55.350 align:middle line:84%
I've thought about
it quite a bit.

00:37:55.350 --> 00:37:56.910 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: I've
thought about it too.

00:37:56.910 --> 00:38:00.160 align:middle line:84%
