00:38:02.470 --> 00:38:04.600 align:middle line:84%
But to know this thing
doesn't necessarily

00:38:04.600 --> 00:38:08.118 align:middle line:84%
represent that, and to still get
the good will of that desire.

00:38:08.118 --> 00:38:09.160 align:middle line:90%
>>HOROWITZ: It's amazing.

00:38:09.160 --> 00:38:13.510 align:middle line:84%
It's like the individual him
or herself, I would venture,

00:38:13.510 --> 00:38:16.990 align:middle line:84%
I would venture, that most
people in our culture today,

00:38:16.990 --> 00:38:18.940 align:middle line:84%
most people if you
say to them, you

00:38:18.940 --> 00:38:21.670 align:middle line:84%
know what the placebo effect
