00:38:21.670 --> 00:38:23.200 align:middle line:84%
Do you believe in
the effectiveness

00:38:23.200 --> 00:38:24.290 align:middle line:90%
of the placebo effect?

00:38:24.290 --> 00:38:25.660 align:middle line:90%
They would say, of course, sure.

00:38:25.660 --> 00:38:28.090 align:middle line:84%
I have read this
and that article.

00:38:28.090 --> 00:38:32.320 align:middle line:84%
The very knowledge that the mind
