So talk about that.

00:43:22.670 --> 00:43:24.140 align:middle line:90%
What are you doing there?

00:43:24.140 --> 00:43:26.990 align:middle line:10%
>>HOROWITZ: Last year,
filmmaker Ronnie Thomas and I

00:43:26.990 --> 00:43:30.710 align:middle line:10%
traveled to Egypt, where we
are shooting a documentary

00:43:30.710 --> 00:43:32.600 align:middle line:10%
on the book, "The
Kybalion" which

00:43:32.600 --> 00:43:36.920 align:middle line:10%
a very wonderful, magical
book it was published in 1908.

00:43:36.920 --> 00:43:41.052 align:middle line:84%
Which is basically a modern
adaptation of Hermetica.

00:43:41.052 --> 00:43:42.260 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Of Hermetica, yeah.

00:43:42.260 --> 00:43:45.350 align:middle line:84%
>>HOROWITZ: So it's the
psychology of the Hermetica.

00:43:45.350 --> 00:43:47.180 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Right,
which would of course,

00:43:47.180 --> 00:43:49.410 align:middle line:84%
have to take you to the
mother country, Egypt.

00:43:49.410 --> 00:43:50.660 align:middle line:90%
>>HOROWITZ: That was our wish.

00:43:50.660 --> 00:43:51.460 align:middle line:90%
That was our wish.

00:43:51.460 --> 00:43:53.390 align:middle line:84%
We said, look, we
don't just want

00:43:53.390 --> 00:43:55.100 align:middle line:84%
to sit in front
of a green screen.

00:43:55.100 --> 00:43:58.350 align:middle line:84%
We really, really want
to go to the source.

00:43:58.350 --> 00:44:02.750 align:middle line:84%
And so we went to Egypt and we
shot there for about two weeks.

00:44:02.750 --> 00:44:05.300 align:middle line:84%
It was an amazing
experience because we

00:44:05.300 --> 00:44:08.060 align:middle line:84%
got to go places that I never
thought I would get to go.

00:44:08.060 --> 00:44:09.980 align:middle line:10%
It was also a very
chaotic experience.

00:44:09.980 --> 00:44:13.460 align:middle line:84%
And I love the nation of Egypt
and I love the Egyptian people.

00:44:13.460 --> 00:44:15.800 align:middle line:84%
It is a tough country
to navigate around in.

00:44:15.800 --> 00:44:20.030 align:middle line:84%
And we had to do a lot to get
places and to get cooperation,

00:44:20.030 --> 00:44:21.380 align:middle line:90%
but we did get cooperation.

00:44:21.380 --> 00:44:24.110 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Did you go to the
main places, like Luxor--

00:44:24.110 --> 00:44:24.770 align:middle line:84%
>>HOROWITZ: Oh, yeah,
we went to the--

00:44:24.770 --> 00:44:25.550 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: --and Ramana.

00:44:25.550 --> 00:44:25.940 align:middle line:90%
>>HOROWITZ: Yeah.

00:44:25.940 --> 00:44:28.280 align:middle line:84%
We went to the main places,
including the Great Pyramids

00:44:28.280 --> 00:44:29.190 align:middle line:90%
and so forth.

00:44:29.190 --> 00:44:31.370 align:middle line:84%
But we got to go to
some places deep, deep

00:44:31.370 --> 00:44:33.620 align:middle line:90%
underneath The Valley of Kings.

00:44:33.620 --> 00:44:35.600 align:middle line:84%
We got to go to some
very out of the way

00:44:35.600 --> 00:44:39.500 align:middle line:84%
places in the Temple of
Karnak, the Karnak complex.

00:44:39.500 --> 00:44:42.350 align:middle line:84%
And I had some
opportunities to lay hands

00:44:42.350 --> 00:44:43.820 align:middle line:84%
on antiquities,
which is something

00:44:43.820 --> 00:44:45.590 align:middle line:90%
that I approach very carefully.

00:44:45.590 --> 00:44:48.890 align:middle line:84%
Because if everybody that comes
along lays hands on something,

00:44:48.890 --> 00:44:50.150 align:middle line:90%
it's going to be ruinous.

00:44:50.150 --> 00:44:52.180 align:middle line:84%
And I thought this
through very carefully.

00:44:52.180 --> 00:44:54.940 align:middle line:84%
But I was given the permission
to do it and I did do it.

00:44:54.940 --> 00:44:57.670 align:middle line:84%
And it was just a physically
tactile, real experience.

00:44:57.670 --> 00:45:00.550 align:middle line:84%
And we talk about, one
of the experiences I had

00:45:00.550 --> 00:45:03.910 align:middle line:84%
was laying hands on a beautiful
magnificent ceremonial bowl.

00:45:03.910 --> 00:45:06.120 align:middle line:84%
And I just felt absolute
lightning course

00:45:06.120 --> 00:45:06.920 align:middle line:90%
through my body.

00:45:06.920 --> 00:45:08.230 align:middle line:84%
There's no other
way I can put it.

00:45:08.230 --> 00:45:09.647 align:middle line:84%
There's no other
way I can put it.

00:45:09.647 --> 00:45:11.170 align:middle line:84%
And you begin to
get a sense of some

00:45:11.170 --> 00:45:14.470 align:middle line:84%
of what the ancient ancestors
might have experienced.

00:45:14.470 --> 00:45:17.740 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And so much
of their iconography

00:45:17.740 --> 00:45:20.380 align:middle line:84%
had to do really with
the movement of the stars

00:45:20.380 --> 00:45:21.280 align:middle line:90%
and the solar system.

00:45:21.280 --> 00:45:22.463 align:middle line:90%
As above, so below.

00:45:22.463 --> 00:45:24.880 align:middle line:84%
>>HOROWITZ: As above, so below,
the great Hermetic dictum.

00:45:24.880 --> 00:45:27.460 align:middle line:84%
And if a person can live
with that statement,

00:45:27.460 --> 00:45:28.420 align:middle line:90%
it sounds so simple.

00:45:28.420 --> 00:45:29.980 align:middle line:90%
As above, so below.

00:45:29.980 --> 00:45:32.380 align:middle line:84%
And yet live with it and
begin to apply it to life,

00:45:32.380 --> 00:45:35.810 align:middle line:84%
and you'll see it begins
to unmask so much to you.

00:45:35.810 --> 00:45:37.060 align:middle line:90%
There's a great power in that.

00:45:37.060 --> 00:45:37.390 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: It really does.

00:45:37.390 --> 00:45:39.460 align:middle line:84%
I mean as soon as you said you
laid your hands on the bowl,

00:45:39.460 --> 00:45:41.080 align:middle line:90%
I'm thinking the Age of Taurus.

00:45:41.080 --> 00:45:43.750 align:middle line:84%
What was happening at that
time and inbued in that.

00:45:43.750 --> 00:45:45.110 align:middle line:90%
>>HOROWITZ: There's so much--

00:45:45.110 --> 00:45:49.110 align:middle line:84%
you know the ancients had such
a profoundly deep understanding

00:45:49.110 --> 00:45:49.910 align:middle line:90%
of nature.

00:45:49.910 --> 00:45:53.350 align:middle line:84%
They were so connected to
nature in ways that I am not,

00:45:53.350 --> 00:45:55.240 align:middle line:84%
I don't think we've
even begun to grapple

00:45:55.240 --> 00:45:57.250 align:middle line:90%
